  <channel>
    <title>Refugees contributor: Marta Foresti</title>
    <description>Marta Foresti is the director of ODI’s Human Mobility Initiative, leading the institute engagement on migration at global, regional and local level. She is visiting senior research fellow at the Institute of Global Affairs and the London School of Economics and she is acting as senior policy advisor for the consultation of the Global Compact For Migration and to the IOM’s Research Syndicate. She is a member of the advisory board of Refugees Deeply, of the editorial board of the Journal of Migration Policy and Practice as well as of the board of PorCausa.org.
</description>
